  <releases>
    <release version="2.12.0" date="2026-01-27">
      <description translate="no">
        <p>Added</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Fine tune the Proxy Method Calls and Actions through the Preferences</li>
          <li>Lazy Start the Proxy</li>
          <li>Refresh the Unit Status on selection</li>
        </ul>
        <p>Fixed</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Fix Flatpak save file in home directory (make a warning)</li>
          <li>Password dialog gets overlapped Sysd Manager on every start  https://github.com/plrigaux/sysd-manager/issues/35</li>
        </ul>
      </description>
    </release>
    <release version="2.11.3" date="2026-01-13">
      <description translate="no">
        <p>Added</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Find text feature on the Unit's Description, File, Dependencies and Journal</li>
          <li>[2.11.1]Find in text can constrain on whole word</li>
          <li>[2.11.3]Toggle display total summary option in the unit list popup menu</li>
          <li>[2.11.4]Menu item to toggle Show Line Numbers on unit file panel.</li>
        </ul>
        <p>Fixed</p>
        <ul>
          <li>[2.11.2]Unit search bar UX improvements (tooltips, icons, sensitivity, ...)</li>
          <li>[2.11.3]Improve Spacing in Top-Bottom Layout https://github.com/plrigaux/sysd-manager/issues/31</li>
        </ul>
      </description>
    </release>
